Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.36,0:00:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rick 在这个宇宙飞船里\N{\fs38}I got to tell you, Rick. It's pretty great
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.14,0:00:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就我们两人 真是挺好的\N{\fs38}To be in this spaceship, just the two of us, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.17,0:00:07.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就到处这样游荡 这风格才对嘛\N{\fs38}Just cruising around, Rick and Morty style.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.00,0:00:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我同意 Morty\N{\fs38}I agree, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.25,0:00:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样返璞归真挺好的\N{\fs38}It's nice to get back to the basics
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.46,0:00:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经过了过去紧张的 混乱的一年\N{\fs38}After a pretty intense, mixed-bag of a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.88,0:00:13.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 哦  - 放松\N{\fs38}- Ohh!  - Relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.90,0:00:15.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挡风玻璃就是干这个用的\N{\fs38}That's what windshields are for.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.30,0:00:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都不知道太空里还有虫子呢\N{\fs38}I didn't know that there were bugs out in space.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.10,0:00:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 那你怎么想的 Morty\N{\fs38}Well, w-what did you think, Morty?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.66,0:00:20.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生命难道是地球自己进化出来的\N{\fs38}Life just developed on earth by itself?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.52,0:00:21.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我处理处理\N{\fs38}Here, let me take care of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.20,0:00:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天呐 Rick 真恶心\N{\fs38}Geez, Rick, that's disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.38,0:00:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想看\N{\fs38}I don't want to look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.38,0:00:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像没有清洁液了\N{\fs38}Yeah, guess I'm out of fluid.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.72,0:00:29.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我找个地方停一下\N{\fs38}L-let me find a place to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.46,0:00:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 你们星球有擦挡风玻璃的清洁液吗\N{\fs38}Hey, muchacho, does your planet have wiper fluid yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.88,0:00:38.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说你们已经吓傻了要把我们当神拜了\N{\fs38}Or are you gonna freak out and start worshipping us?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.76,0:00:41.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 杂货店里应该有你要的东西  - 谢谢\N{\fs38}- The general store ought to have what you need. - Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.40,0:00:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你肯定想要在日落前离开这里\N{\fs38}Of course, you'll be wanting to be gone from here by sundown.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.14,0:00:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 当然 等一下 什么 为什么啊\N{\fs38}Yeah, sure thing. Wait a minute. What? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.40,0:00:48.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日落以后节日就开始了\N{\fs38}Sundown is when the festival begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.46,0:00:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,节日\N{\fs38}The festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.54,0:00:52.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦哦 好吧 对于我们Millennia人来说\N{\fs38}Ooh, well, for Millennia,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.10,0:00:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的社会已经完全没有犯罪和战争了\N{\fs38}Our society has been free of crime and war,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.02,0:00:57.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我们生活在和平之中  - 哦 我知道这是什么了\N{\fs38}- Living in perfect peace.  - Oh, I know what this is!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.54,0:00:59.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们维持世界和平\N{\fs38}You've been able to sustain world peace
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.10,0:01:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠的是每年有一天晚上 能到处\N{\fs38}Because you have one night a year where you all run around
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.38,0:01:03.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抢劫杀人 还不用承担任何后果\N{\fs38}Robbing and murdering each other without consequence.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.40,0:01:04.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 是这样的  - 什么\N{\fs38}- That's right. - What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.46,0:01:06.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像是<人类清除计划>那电影 Morty\N{\fs38}It's like "The purge," Morty. That movie "The purge"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.68,0:01:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 你以前来过这里么\N{\fs38}Oh, have you been here before?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.16,0:01:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不 但是我去过好几个星球都有这样的东西\N{\fs38}No, no, but I've been to a few planets with the same gimmick.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.30,0:01:13.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道么 有时候这事也叫作"大净化"或者"红色时间"\N{\fs38}You know, sometimes it's called "the cleansing" or "the red time".
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.14,0:01:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这么个世界就直接管这叫"杀人夜"\N{\fs38}There was this one world that called it just murder night.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.38,0:01:16.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这是个搞大清除的星球\N{\fs38}I-it's a purge planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.84,0:01:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们一片和平 然后 他们搞清除\N{\fs38}They're peaceful, and then, you know, they just purge.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.12,0:01:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也太可怕了\N{\fs38}T-that's horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.42,0:01:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊\N{\fs38}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.18,0:01:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想看看么\N{\fs38}You want to check it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.68,0:01:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 你在节日上一般都干什么啊\N{\fs38}So, what do you do during the festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.20,0:01:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是把自己锁在屋里 还是出去干点什么呀\N{\fs38}You lock yourself in, or you go out and do some stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.50,0:02:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 我干一些很坏很坏的事\N{\fs38}Oh, I do some pretty bad stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.82,0:02:03.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 我估计也是 老爷子\N{\fs38}Oh, I bet you do, old timer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.24,0:02:06.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天呐 Rick 快走吧 太阳快下山了\N{\fs38}Gee— Rick, come on. The sun is setting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.40,0:02:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们得离开这里啊\N{\fs38}W-we got to get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.80,0:02:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 好吧 这个玻璃清洗液多少钱\N{\fs38}All right, well, w-what do I owe you for the wiper fluid?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.84,0:02:12.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,免费的 哦 还有\N{\fs38}It's on the house. Oh, and, uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.24,0:02:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你再拿点糖吧 \N{\fs38}Why— why don't you have some candy bars, as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.70,0:02:16.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 不会吧 你真好\N{\fs38}Oh, no way. That's really nice of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.54,0:02:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是个好人 至少现在是\N{\fs38}I'm a nice guy... for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.90,0:02:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦 这我不怀疑\N{\fs38}Ohh, I don't doubt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.72,0:02:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Rick  - 好啦好啦 \N{\fs38}- Rick!  - Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.20,0:02:24.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 节日上好好玩呀 老爷子\N{\fs38}Hey, have a good festival, old timer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.22,0:02:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是这么打算的\N{\fs38}I intend to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.60,0:02:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rick 快开门\N{\fs38}Rick, unlock it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.90,0:02:31.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就等一下 Morty\N{\fs38}Just a second, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.14,0:02:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 快看那夕阳\N{\fs38}Oh, look at that sunset.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.96,0:02:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别闹了\N{\fs38}Stop screwing around.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.44,0:02:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 好多了 现在能看清楚了\N{\fs38}There we go. Much better. Now we can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.08,0:02:39.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵\N{\fs38}Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.92,0:02:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 Morty\N{\fs38}Hey, you know what, Morty?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.92,0:02:43.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在玻璃已经擦得锃光瓦亮了\N{\fs38}Why don't we christen our squeaky-clean windshield here
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.00,0:02:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们正好看看大清楚怎么样\N{\fs38}By watching a little of this purge through it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.96,0:02:47.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 不 你有病么\N{\fs38}What?! No! What is your problem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.90,0:02:49.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Morty 成熟点吧 你要是不想看\N{\fs38}Morty, grow up. If you don't want to watch,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.68,0:02:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就别看 但是 你知道 这是我的车\N{\fs38}Don't watch, but, you know, it's my car.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.52,0:02:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 你要是告诉你妈\N{\fs38}Also, if you tell your mom about this,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.46,0:02:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我就把你给清除了  - 你太差劲了\N{\fs38}- I'll purge you.  - You're the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.10,0:02:57.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个星球也是 你怎么会喜欢这种东西\N{\fs38}And this planet is the worst. How can you be into this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.38,0:02:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看这种互相残杀的戏码\N{\fs38}You know, people are gonna kill each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.84,0:03:00.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 你坐这儿就是想告诉我\N{\fs38}So, what, y-y-you trying to sit here and tell me that
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.36,0:03:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有个在线视频\N{\fs38}I-if -- if there's a video online
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.18,0:03:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内容是有人被砍头的那种\N{\fs38}With someone getting decapitated,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.46,0:03:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 难道你不会点进去看看  - 不\N{\fs38}- You don't click on it?  - No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.76,0:03:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊 为什么我要点进去看啊 你为什么要看啊\N{\fs38}Why— why would I do that? You do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.96,0:03:09.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不看 因为太无聊了\N{\fs38}I don't, because it would bore me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.42,0:03:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃早点的时候才看那种[哔]玩意儿 Morty\N{\fs38}I see [bleep] like that for breakfast, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.26,0:03:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你不点进去看 我说就是因为\N{\fs38}But if you don't do it, I say it's because
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.86,0:03:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你惧怕你的原始冲动\N{\fs38}You're afraid of your own primal instincts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.60,0:03:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你极力压制他们然后\N{\fs38}So you stuff them down and—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.94,0:03:17.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 哦 嘘 嘘 开始了\N{\fs38}OH, OH! Shh. Shh. It's starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.53,0:03:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 哦吼吼 开始啦  - 我不看\N{\fs38}- Oh-ho-ho! Here we go.  - I'm not watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.92,0:03:21.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好 好 你的奖牌已经寄家去了\N{\fs38}Yeah, yeah, yeah, your medal's in the mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.48,0:03:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我要离近点看  - 哦 好吧 随便\N{\fs38}- I'm gonna get a closer look. - Oh, okay, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.38,0:03:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下就会有人扔石头\N{\fs38}And then someone's gonna throw a rock
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.62,0:03:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打中我们的车 然后车子坠毁\N{\fs38}And hit the car and then we're gonna crash
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.30,0:03:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我们就困在下面了\N{\fs38}And we're gonna be stuck down there
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.48,0:03:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的就都是我们活该了\N{\fs38}And it's gonna be what we deserve.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.60,0:03:35.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 这真是[哔]的互相残杀\N{\fs38}Whoa, they are purging the [bleep] out of each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.96,0:03:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦我的天呐\N{\fs38}Oh, my god!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.78,0:03:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦[哔]\N{\fs38}Oh [bleep]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.98,0:03:42.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是 好吧 那真是恶心\N{\fs38}That was— okay, yeah. T-that was gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.06,0:03:45.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来我的胃还是没有我的眼睛坚强\N{\fs38}Man, I think my eyes were bigger than my stomach
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.72,0:03:47.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不太了这个 Morty\N{\fs38}On this one, Morty. Ugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.26,0:03:49.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对杀戮的观赏欲一瞬间就已经满足了\N{\fs38}My appetite for purge-spectating got filled pretty quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.78,0:03:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦天呐\N{\fs38}Oh, god.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.74,0:03:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离我远点\N{\fs38}Get away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.00,0:03:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不 救命\N{\fs38}No! No! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.30,0:03:59.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快来人救我呀 啊\N{\fs38}Somebody help me! Aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.66,0:04:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 Morty 咱 咱们走吧\N{\fs38}All right, Morty. L-let's get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.29,0:04:03.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 等一下 我们得下去\N{\fs38}Wait, wait, wait. Hold on. W-we have to go down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.84,0:04:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 为什么啊\N{\fs38}What? Why?
