Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.72,0:04:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫Morty 这是我外公\N{\fs38}My name is Morty. This is my grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.90,0:04:33.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我们是来旅游的  - 不再是了\N{\fs38}- We're tourists.  - Not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.84,0:04:37.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦天呐 这太[哔]爽了\N{\fs38}Oh, my god. This is [bleep] awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.86,0:04:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Morty 这太酷了\N{\fs38}Morty, this is really cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.46,0:04:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 你 你想帮我杀几个人不\N{\fs38}Hey, y-you want to help me out here and kill some people?
