Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.90,0:04:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们是为了救一个小女孩啊\N{\fs38}Because we're saving a little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.26,0:04:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说 这些人我们可以随便杀 完全没问题\N{\fs38}I mean, w-w-we're both free and clear to murder these people.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.14,0:04:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你没事吧  - 是的\N{\fs38}- Are you okay?  - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.96,0:04:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得找个地方躲一下\N{\fs38}I have to find somewhere to hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.34,0:04:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 你可以和我们一起啊 Rick\N{\fs38}Well, you can hide with us. Rick?
