Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.02,0:04:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你 你叫什么名字  - Arthrisha\N{\fs38}- W-what's your name?  - Arthrisha.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.56,0:04:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以带Arthrisha上车么\N{\fs38}Could we take Arthrisha up in the ship
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.50,0:04:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 你懂的 就等着大清除结束\N{\fs38}And, you know, just wait out the purge?
