Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.40,0:05:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也能阻止犯罪么 到底什么原理啊" 那样的\N{\fs38}This is gonna stop crime how, exactly?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.70,0:05:25.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 最开始人们花了不少时间接受这件事\N{\fs38}Yeah, it took some time for people to accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.72,0:05:27.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我猜也是\N{\fs38}Yeah, I bet. I bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.32,0:05:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊有点像手机\N{\fs38}Yeah, it's kind of like cellphones, you know?
