Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.66,0:05:48.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你是认真在问我  - 就是想聊聊天\N{\fs38}- Is that a real question? - Just making conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.64,0:05:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么 你说的哪句话让我能接着聊下去啊\N{\fs38}Are you? What part of that gives me anything to work with?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.54,0:05:54.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的选择要么是不作回答 要么冷嘲热讽\N{\fs38}My choice is to say nothing, be sarcastic,
