Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.36,0:06:16.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 没事的\N{\fs38}All right, hey, hey, that's cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.20,0:06:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没关系的\N{\fs38}I can roll with that.
