Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.92,0:06:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我外婆 我们得救她\N{\fs38}My nana! We have to save her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.90,0:06:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚想起来你外婆还在呢\N{\fs38}You just now remembered your nana exists.
