Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.46,0:08:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我听不清楚  - 谁啊\N{\fs38}- I can barely hear you. - Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.01,0:08:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟Morty在一个正在搞大清除的星球\N{\fs38}Morty and I are on a planet that's purging.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.81,0:08:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你要记下  - 什么锡球\N{\fs38}- I need you to take down... - A plan that's what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.01,0:08:46.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在一个正在大清除的星球 大清除\N{\fs38}We're on a planet that's purging, Summer. Purging.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.26,0:08:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的飞船和枪都被抢走了 我们正在一场大清除中\N{\fs38}We lost our car and my gun, and we're in a purge.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.44,0:08:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Taddi Mason打来的吗\N{\fs38}Ooh, is it Taddi Mason?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.67,0:08:51.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像那部电影一样吗\N{\fs38}Like the movie "The purge"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.16,0:08:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 你得记\N{\fs38}Yes, I- I need you to take...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.31,0:08:53.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那部电影烂透了\N{\fs38}That movie sucked.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.45,0:08:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天呐 等一下\N{\fs38}Oh, my god. Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.20,0:08:56.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是Taddi Mason吗\N{\fs38}It's not Taddi Mason?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.36,0:08:58.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸 Taddi Mason[哔]是谁\N{\fs38}Dad, who the [bleep] is Taddi Mason?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.35,0:08:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 一个朋友  - 啊\N{\fs38}- My friend. - Aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.20,0:09:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吗 我开免提了\N{\fs38}Are you okay? I'm putting you on speaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.21,0:09:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Taddi吗  - 是啊Jerry 我是Taddi\N{\fs38}- Taddi? - Yes, Jerry, it's Taddi,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.06,0:09:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前从来没人听说过的人\N{\fs38}A person no one's ever heard of until now,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.71,0:09:06.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正拿太空电话打给你呢\N{\fs38}Calling you on a space phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.20,0:09:07.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我分不出你是不是在讽刺\N{\fs38}I can't tell if you're being sarcastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.80,0:09:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装弹 赶快\N{\fs38}Reload, fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.01,0:09:17.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Summer 你得记下这串数字\N{\fs38}Summer, w- we need you to take down this number.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.14,0:09:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 别扯别的  - Morty吗 你没事吧\N{\fs38}- Quit screwing around. - Morty? Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.51,0:09:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 当然有事  - 你怎么和Taddi Mason在一起\N{\fs38}- No! - Why are you with Taddi Mason?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.76,0:09:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我[哔] 你[哔]闭嘴吧老爸\N{\fs38}Holy [bleep] Dad! Shut the [bleep] up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.87,0:09:27.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧看来 我就是全家人的出气筒\N{\fs38}Okay. I guess I'm just this entire family's toilet paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.06,0:09:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有在记吗 快把数字记下来\N{\fs38}Are you writing this down? Will you please write this down?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.31,0:09:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 好好  - 7 7 1 9 8\N{\fs38}- Yes, yes. - 7, 7, 1, 9, 8...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.90,0:09:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3 6 4 2 1 1 2 5\N{\fs38}3, 6, 4, 2, 1, 1, 2, 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.35,0:09:43.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这狗日的\N{\fs38}You son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.98,0:09:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Morty 我也不想求助\N{\fs38}Morty, I don't want to be the "A little help" Guy,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.96,0:09:47.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你能搭把手吗\N{\fs38}But a little help?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.58,0:09:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我找到笔了 说\N{\fs38}Okay, I have a pen. Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.73,0:09:54.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7 7 1 9 8 3 6 4 2 1 1 2 5\N{\fs38}7, 7, 1, 9, 8, 3, 6, 4, 2, 1, 1, 2, 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.88,0:09:55.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就给我个勺子吗\N{\fs38}A spoon, Morty?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.64,0:09:57.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你搞什么  - 对不起\N{\fs38}- A spoon?! - I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.11,0:09:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你旁边这么多餐具\N{\fs38}There's a pile of silverware next to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:10:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我个最没杀伤力的东西\N{\fs38}And you throw me the one thing that can never kill anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.31,0:10:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我错了还不行吗\N{\fs38}All right, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.31,0:10:05.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,车库里我工作台上有个架子\N{\fs38}Summer, on the shelf above my workbench in the garage,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.14,0:10:07.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一个带键盘的红盒子\N{\fs38}There's a red box with a keypad on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.10,0:10:08.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把盒子拿到外面\N{\fs38}You're gonna take that box outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.56,0:10:10.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,输入我刚才给你报的数字\N{\fs38}and you're gonna type the number I just gave you into the keypad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.67,0:10:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 明白吗  - 明白\N{\fs38}- Got it? - Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.72,0:10:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恨自己的老爸是成长的一部分吗\N{\fs38}Is it just part of growing up to hate your dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.21,0:10:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懒得搭理你\N{\fs38}I'm ignoring you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.40,0:10:18.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我能到那个灯塔顶上\N{\fs38}Morty, if I can get to the top of that lighthouse,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.43,0:10:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以发射信标 你姐就能把东西送过来\N{\fs38}I can send the beacon, and your sister can launch our package.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.78,0:10:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记住了 如果那里有人\N{\fs38}Just remember, if there's people in there
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.39,0:10:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且他们想杀我们的话 我们先把他们弄死\N{\fs38}And they try to purge us, we got to purge them first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.47,0:10:27.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们谁也不弄死 Rick 能不能别这样\N{\fs38}We're not purging anyone, Rick, all right? W- will you stop it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.26,0:10:28.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果还想看见明天的太阳\N{\fs38}Morty, if we're gonna survive tonight,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.61,0:10:30.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得学会驾驭你压抑的愤怒\N{\fs38}You're gonna need to harness your repressed rage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.48,0:10:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有压抑的愤怒\N{\fs38}I don't have any!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.31,0:10:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这语气就挺压抑的\N{\fs38}Spoken like a person with repressed rage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.15,0:10:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有参加节日\N{\fs38}I take no part in the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.74,0:10:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你们想杀我 只求下手麻利点\N{\fs38}If you desire to kill me, I only ask you do it quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.94,0:10:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没这个打算\N{\fs38}No such agenda, chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.24,0:10:45.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们对大清除也没什么兴趣\N{\fs38}We're not too keen on the purge, either, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.29,0:10:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只想到你灯塔顶上\N{\fs38}We were just hoping to get on the roof of your lighthouse
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.31,0:10:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为我在地球的姐姐设一个信标\N{\fs38}So we can send a beacon to my sister on earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.37,0:10:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 那是另外一个星球  - 顺便说一句\N{\fs38}- It's a different planet. - By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.97,0:10:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别的星球也存在生命 不过重点不在这儿\N{\fs38}Life on other planets exists. Don't let it distract you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.41,0:10:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们可以藏在我的灯塔里 设信标\N{\fs38}I'll let you use my lighthouse for shelter and beacon-sending
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.07,0:10:57.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过条件是 你们得听听我写的故事剧本\N{\fs38}On the condition that you listen to my tale.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.78,0:10:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 好  - 成交\N{\fs38}- Okay. - Deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.86,0:11:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去楼顶把东西弄好\N{\fs38}All right, I'm gonna go to the roof and set things up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.74,0:11:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Morty 你听他读  - 好\N{\fs38}- Morty, you listen to his tale. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.98,0:11:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"镜头淡入 外景 不知名的城市 白天"\N{\fs38}"Fade in. Exterior. Unnamed city. Day."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.05,0:11:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"进步的路上 熙熙攘攘"\N{\fs38}"The hustle and bustle is a symphony of progress."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.06,0:11:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"镜头略过形形色色的窗户 每扇中都是一个故事"\N{\fs38}"We pan past windows, each of which contain a different story,"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.77,0:11:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"最终定格在Jacey Lakims身上"\N{\fs38}"To find Jacey Lakims,"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.91,0:11:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"这个年方二八的惹火少妇丝毫没有意识到自己的美丽"\N{\fs38}"28, hot, but doesn't know it."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.81,0:11:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Jacey不得不停了下来"\N{\fs38}"Jacey stops when her high heel gets caught"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.43,0:11:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"因为高跟鞋卡在了下水道格栅里"\N{\fs38}"In the grating of a sewer."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.68,0:11:27.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"突然一个男人出现 用枪指着她"\N{\fs38}"Suddenly, a man steps into frame and points a gun at her."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.64,0:11:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"她今天不走运"\N{\fs38}"This is not her day."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.05,0:11:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"镜头淡入黑暗"\N{\fs38}"Fade to black."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.45,0:11:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几个字浮现 "三周前"\N{\fs38}Title--'three weeks earlier'.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.27,0:11:39.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的不想谈谈吗\N{\fs38}You really don't want to talk to me about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.11,0:11:41.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸 外公和Morty情况危险\N{\fs38}Dad, grandpa and Morty are in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.42,0:11:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你 正失业中 只是无聊\N{\fs38}You're unemployed, and you're bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.24,0:11:45.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 孰轻孰重自有分晓  - 别再说失业的事好吗\N{\fs38}- They're a higher priority. - Stop saying I'm unemployed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.87,0:11:50.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7 7 1 9 8 3 6 4 2 1 1 2 5\N{\fs38}Okay, 7, 7, 1, 9, 8, 3, 6, 4, 2, 1, 1, 2, 5
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.21,0:11:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事\N{\fs38}Aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.58,0:11:52.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这什么东西 又闹哪出\N{\fs38}Good lord! Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.20,0:11:57.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着 我是你的父亲 我只是想说 我是爱你的\N{\fs38}Look, I'm your father, and I love you is all I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.36,0:11:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 仅此而已  - 说完你就满意了吧\N{\fs38}- I'll leave it at that. - Fine, dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.25,0:12:04.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外公好像说过要先拿到外面去\N{\fs38}Oh, he might have said to take it outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.28,0:12:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点啊 Summer\N{\fs38}Come on, Summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.09,0:12:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往盒子上输几个数字有什么难的\N{\fs38}How hard is it to type some numbers into a box?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.51,0:12:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标锁定\N{\fs38}Target locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.21,0:12:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢天谢地\N{\fs38}Oh, thank god.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.56,0:12:13.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟Summer这边都万事俱备\N{\fs38}Well, I did my job. Summer did her job.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.43,0:12:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只欠Morty听完他的剧本了\N{\fs38}Now all Morty has to do is finish listening to that tale.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.30,0:12:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Blaine说"可能我不需要新朋友"\N{\fs38}Blaine: Maybe I don't need a new friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.46,0:12:21.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jacey说"可能你是我唯一需要的朋友"\N{\fs38}Jacey: Maybe you're the only friend I need.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.94,0:12:23.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Blaine说"需要还是想要"\N{\fs38}Blaine: Need, or want?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.16,0:12:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jacey说"我从未如此渴望过"\N{\fs38}Jacey: I've never been much for wanting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.57,0:12:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Blaine "这语气像是有迫切需求的人"\N{\fs38}Blaine: Spoken like someone with needs."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.84,0:12:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 老天爷  - 什么\N{\fs38}- Oh, geez. - Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.04,0:12:31.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 请 请继续\N{\fs38}Uh, sorry. K-keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.04,0:12:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Jacey伸手拂过他的脸颊"\N{\fs38}"Jacey reaches out and touches his face."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.00,0:12:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"很明显他所需正是她所想"\N{\fs38}"It's clear he needs what she wants."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.62,0:12:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"男女相遇 干柴烈火"\N{\fs38}"She's a woman. He's a man."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.96,0:12:39.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"他将她揽入怀中 城市废墟在身后熊熊燃烧"\N{\fs38}"The city burns in the background as he takes her in his arms."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.96,0:12:40.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"镜头淡出"\N{\fs38}"Fade out."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.15,0:12:42.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几个字浮现 "剧终"\N{\fs38}Title--'The End'.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.18,0:12:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"再加个问号"\N{\fs38}"Question mark."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.06,0:12:45.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 哇  - 可以吧\N{\fs38}- Wow. - Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.61,0:12:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真是 不错 写得好\N{\fs38}It's...g-good job. Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.41,0:12:50.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你喜欢吗  - 当然喜欢\N{\fs38}- You liked it? - Of course I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.11,0:12:51.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酒吧那部分你没有笑\N{\fs38}You didn't laugh at the scene in the bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.44,0:12:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那段挺搞笑的 但是我想听后面的部分\N{\fs38}I...thought it was funny, but I wanted to hear the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.11,0:12:56.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么想法吗 意见呢\N{\fs38}Do you have any thoughts? Notes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.92,0:12:59.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 仅仅是乐在其中\N{\fs38}No. I-I just enjoyed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.06,0:13:01.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我的意见 请再多写一点\N{\fs38}That's my note, you know? Please write more.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.31,0:13:03.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 感觉你在敷衍  - 不不\N{\fs38}- Seems a little insincere. - What? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.34,0:13:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用好言哄我\N{\fs38}You don't have to mollycoddle me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.70,0:13:07.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想改进我的写作 说出你的真实想法\N{\fs38}I want to improve my writing. Tell me your real thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.06,0:13:10.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 呃 从我个人角度来说\N{\fs38}All right. Well, um, I'm not a huge fan, personally,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.44,0:13:12.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是很喜欢那个"三周前"开场戏的倒叙\N{\fs38}Of the whole "Three weeks earlier" teaser thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.54,0:13:13.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得\N{\fs38}I feel like, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.52,0:13:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该从故事开始的地方下笔\N{\fs38}We should start our stories where they begin.
