Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.38,0:18:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能还是一首冠单\N{\fs38}Topped the charts, I think. HO, HO!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.77,0:18:42.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,*感觉很好*\N{\fs38}*Oh, it feels good.*
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.69,0:18:45.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢你的帮助 Rick\N{\fs38}Hey, thanks for helping me, Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.36,0:18:46.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是个好人\N{\fs38}You're a pretty great guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.77,0:18:48.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[哔]你射爆我的肝\N{\fs38}Yeah, yeah, yeah. [bleep] you for shooting my liver.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.91,0:18:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有机会再见\N{\fs38}I'll see you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.16,0:18:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊 发生了什么事\N{\fs38}Oh, man. What -- what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.80,0:18:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心 Morty\N{\fs38}Don't worry about it, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.90,0:18:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了 如果你想打一炮的话\N{\fs38}Listen, if you wanted to try to get a piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.62,0:18:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行动起来 最后的机会了\N{\fs38}You better hurry up. Now's your last chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.40,0:19:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arthrisha 可能我\N{\fs38}Hey, hey, Arthrisha, um, maybe I could --
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.96,0:19:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有男朋友了\N{\fs38}Uh, I have a boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.04,0:19:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 好吧  - 我不是想冒犯你\N{\fs38}- Okay. - I'm not trying to be rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.76,0:19:05.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是不想你误会\N{\fs38}I just -- I don't want to lead you on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.53,0:19:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂的\N{\fs38}I-I-I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.66,0:19:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常感谢你帮忙终结了这个节日\N{\fs38}I mean, thank you so much for helping end the festival,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.54,0:19:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我已经有男朋友了 他只是\N{\fs38}But I have a boyfriend, and, uh, he's just --
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.76,0:19:14.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 你不用再说下去了\N{\fs38}Okay, okay, you can stop saying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.30,0:19:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你第一次说的时候我就懂了\N{\fs38}I took it okay the first time,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.60,0:19:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用再说了\N{\fs38}And now you're just repeating stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.24,0:19:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 很抱歉  - 没事\N{\fs38}- oh, I'm sorry. - it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.87,0:19:22.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很好人 但我不能\N{\fs38}Oh, you're so sweet, I just -- oh, but I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.41,0:19:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还在说\N{\fs38}Yeah, you're still doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.12,0:19:27.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从头开始建设一个社会不容易\N{\fs38}It won't be easy creating a new society from the ground up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.80,0:19:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简单有效的原则 想要什么就去弄什么\N{\fs38}Well, a helpful rule might be if you need something, you get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.92,0:19:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 很简单 对吧  - 我需要食物\N{\fs38}- pretty simple, right? - I need food.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.85,0:19:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 谁有给这家伙的食物  - 我有 但那是我的\N{\fs38}- who's got food for that guy? - I do, but this is for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.92,0:19:37.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能多做点食物吗\N{\fs38}Can't you make some more?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.24,0:19:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然可以 我为所有人做食物的时候\N{\fs38}Oh, sure. And while I'm making food for everyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.86,0:19:41.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁来照顾我的孩子呢\N{\fs38}Who takes care of my kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.63,0:19:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来帮你照顾孩子 前提是我要有额外的食物\N{\fs38}I'll take care of your kids, if I get some extra food for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.18,0:19:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,额外的食物\N{\fs38}Extra food?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.34,0:19:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人人所得一样的话 我可不会花额外的功夫\N{\fs38}Well, I'm not gonna do extra work if we all get the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.24,0:19:51.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 公平至上\N{\fs38}All right, okay, fair is fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.61,0:19:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多劳者多得\N{\fs38}If you do extra work, you get extra food.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.34,0:19:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那谁来记下\N{\fs38}Who's gonna keep track
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.68,0:19:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个人"劳"多少"得"多少呢\N{\fs38}Of who gets how much food for how much work?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.45,0:20:00.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 我可以\N{\fs38}Hello. I can do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.72,0:20:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来记录每个人应得的食物\N{\fs38}I'll keep track of everyone's food,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.72,0:20:04.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用来换取食物\N{\fs38}You know, in exchange for food.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.45,0:20:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那根本不是真正的工作\N{\fs38}That's not a real job!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.82,0:20:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道做食物就是吗\N{\fs38}Oh, and making food is?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.20,0:20:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你个混蛋\N{\fs38}You son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.42,0:20:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尝尝这招\N{\fs38}Eat this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.74,0:20:15.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 伙计们\N{\fs38}Guys, guys, guys, guys, whoa, whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.12,0:20:18.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淡定点 别激动\N{\fs38}Cool it, now. Take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.64,0:20:20.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么好战\N{\fs38}There's too much aggression here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.79,0:20:22.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不我们制定一段时间\N{\fs38}What if we designate a period of time
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.00,0:20:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽情释放我们\N{\fs38}During which we can all get this hate, murder,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.02,0:20:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内心的憎恨 杀欲和愤怒\N{\fs38}And rage out of our system --
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.60,0:20:30.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很惭愧\N{\fs38}I can't help but feel ashamed
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.96,0:20:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天居然干了这种事 Rick\N{\fs38}About what I did back there, Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.44,0:20:34.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是对的 我的内心太压抑了\N{\fs38}I guess you were right. I've got a lot of repressed stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.64,0:20:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我需要好好处理 - 别担心 Morty\N{\fs38}- I need to deal with. - Don't worry about it, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.48,0:20:37.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还记得那些糖吗\N{\fs38}Remember those candy bars earlier
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.98,0:20:40.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我们刚来的时候拿的那些  - 怎么了\N{\fs38}- that we got in the first act? - yeah, what about them?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.46,0:20:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来它们含有一种化学成分叫"清除醇"\N{\fs38}Turns out they have a chemical in them called purgenol
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.68,0:20:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种物质会加重你的暴力倾向\N{\fs38}That amplifies all your violent tendencies.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.81,0:20:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊 真是感谢天感谢地\N{\fs38}Oh, boy. Whew! Thank goodness for that, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.20,0:20:48.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松了一口气\N{\fs38}That's a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.12,0:20:49.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 冷汗都不用冒一滴\N{\fs38}Yep. Don't even sweat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.62,0:20:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是那个Morty\N{\fs38}You're still the same old Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.94,0:20:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的人格没有受到损害\N{\fs38}Your character's totally protected.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.68,0:20:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(现在不含清除醇)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.67,0:21:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jerry 什么是"Taddi Mason llc"\N{\fs38}Jerry, what is "Taddi Mason llc,"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.94,0:21:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有为什么电话费要七百块\N{\fs38}And why is our phone bill $700?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.11,0:21:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很无聊吗\N{\fs38}Uh... hey, are you bored...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.99,0:21:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你孤单吗 只想找个朋友\N{\fs38}Uh... ...lonely, just looking for a friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.53,0:21:41.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打给我吧 Taddi Mason\N{\fs38}Uh... call me, taddi mason.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.33,0:21:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每分钟1.99元而已\N{\fs38}It's only $1.99 a minute to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.22,0:21:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天注册\N{\fs38}Uh... sign up today,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.36,0:21:46.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还会定期打给你\N{\fs38}And I'll even call you on a regular basis...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.62,0:21:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是每分钟1.99元\N{\fs38}Uh... ...for just $1.99 a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.12,0:21:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,划算极了 我是一个好朋友\N{\fs38}That's a steal because I'm a great pal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.64,0:21:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以谈体育 谈烧烤\N{\fs38}Uh... we could talk about sports or barbecue.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.38,0:21:56.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jerry 快找份工作\N{\fs38}Jerry, get a job.
